According to the scholars of Woodhurst, the relics were likely stolen by a group of bandits who have overrun the abandoned mining camp in the Hills of Delvenaugh.

Description_42_B07608C54B81CD8D2C16ABBCA.SourceString: Travellers to Arema are being attacked by Vampires. A priest by the name of Father Aubrey informed me that a Chapter Paladin by the name of Leon Harfort has been following leads on the whereabouts of the Vampires. I should speak with him.

Description_42_B07608C54B81CD8D2C16ABBCA.SourceString: My vision came true. I should return to Geoffrey and see what I should do next.

Description_42_B07608C54B81CD8D2C16ABBCA.SourceString: Now that you know that your visions are true, it is up to you to prove yourself to the world. Geoffrey suggested that I should start in Elderglen and grow my reputation there.
